{
  "module": "08-lifecycle-resources.md",
  "group": "08 — Lifecycle & Resources (生命周期与资源)",
  "apiCount": 7,
  "apis": [
    {
      "name": "UIAbility",
      "purpose": "带界面的应用组件，提供onCreate/onForeground/onBackground/onDestroy生命周期回调及后台通信能力",
      "anchor": "uiability",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "UIAbilityContext",
      "purpose": "UIAbility组件的上下文，继承自Context，提供startAbility/terminateSelf/startAbilityForResult等方法",
      "anchor": "uiabilitycontext",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "AbilityConstant",
      "purpose": "Ability启动相关常量，如LaunchReason/LastExitReason/LaunchParam等枚举和数据结构",
      "anchor": "abilityconstant",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "common (Context)",
      "purpose": "Ability Kit公共类型模块，导出UIAbilityContext/Context/ApplicationContext/AbilityResult等类型别名",
      "anchor": "abilityconstant",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "$r / $m",
      "purpose": "$r: 获取应用或系统资源的Resource对象（内置全局函数）。$m在本地文档库中未作为运行时API存在，仅做module.json5配置语法使用",
      "anchor": "r",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "ResourceManager",
      "purpose": "资源管理，提供getStringSync/getMediaContentSync/getDrawableDescriptor/getConfigurationSync等方法",
      "anchor": "resourcemanager",
      "status": "found"
    },
    {
      "name": "@ohos.i18n",
      "purpose": "国际化和本地化，提供Calendar/TimeZone/PhoneNumberFormat/SimpleDateTimeFormat等类",
      "anchor": "i18n",
      "status": "found"
    }
  ],
  "notableFindings": [
    "$m 在本地文档库中未作为运行时API存在，module.json5中的 $media: 是配置级语法，非可调用函数",
    "ResourceManager 在 Stage 模型下通过 context.resourceManager 直接访问，无需手动 import",
    "ECMA 402 标准国际化（Intl.DateTimeFormat 等）位于 @ohos.intl，部分已废弃，建议优先使用 @ohos.i18n",
    "UIAbilityContext 可通过 import { common } from '@kit.AbilityKit' 导入获得类型声明",
    "AbilityConstant 作为单独模块导入 (import { AbilityConstant } from '@kit.AbilityKit')，其 LaunchParam 是 onCreate 回调的必要参数"
  ],
  "missingApis": []
}
